TI  - Carbon sequestration and turnover in semiarid savannas and dry forest
T2  - CLIMATIC CHANGE
KW  - C-sequestration
KW  - mitigation
KW  - semiarid tropics
KW  - SOIL ORGANIC-MATTER
KW  - PRIMARY PRODUCTIVITY
