TI  - Soil microbial biomass and organic carbon in reforested sites degraded by bauxite mining in the Amazon
T2  - TOWARDS SUSTAINABLE LAND USE, VOLS I & II: FURTHERING COOPERATION BETWEEN PEOPLE AND INSTITUTIONS
KW  - microbial biomass
