TI  - Observations of albedo and radiation balance over postforest land surfaces in the eastern Amazon Basin
T2  - JOURNAL OF CLIMATE
KW  - TROPICAL DEFORESTATION
KW  - CLIMATE CHANGE
KW  - FOREST
KW  - VEGETATION
