TI  - Pasture burning in Amazonia: Dynamics of residual biomass and the storage and release of aboveground carbon
T2  - JOURNAL OF GEOPHYSICAL RESEARCH-ATMOSPHERES
KW  - BIOSPHERE
KW  - TROPICS
KW  - DIOXIDE
