TI  - PHYSIOLOGICAL-RESPONSES TO SOIL-MOISTURE STRESS IN 2 AMAZONIAN GAP-INVADER SPECIES
T2  - FUNCTIONAL ECOLOGY
KW  - AMAZON
KW  - BRAZIL
